{
  "id": "anova_one_way",
  "type": "interactive",
  "subject": "statistics_probability",
  "title_en": "One-Way ANOVA",
  "title_he": "ניתוח שונות חד-כיווני (ANOVA)",
  "duration_min": 40,
  "level_min": "university",
  "agent_hints": "Students confuse ANOVA with multiple t-tests. A significant F only means some group differs; use post-hoc tests for pairs.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "purpose_hypotheses",
      "title_en": "Purpose and Hypotheses",
      "title_he": "מטרה והשערות",
      "level_min": "university",
      "body_en_md": "**One-way ANOVA** tests whether **population means of $k \\ge 3$ groups** are equal.\n\n$$H_0: \\mu_1 = \\mu_2 = \\cdots = \\mu_k$$\n\n$$H_a: \\text{at least one } \\mu_i \\text{ differs}$$",
      "body_he_md": "**ANOVA חד-כיווני** בודק שוויון ממוצעי $k \\ge 3$ קבוצות.\n\n$$H_0: \\mu_1 = \\mu_2 = \\cdots = \\mu_k$$"
    },
    {
      "id": "partitioning_variance",
      "title_en": "Partitioning Total Variance",
      "title_he": "פירוק שונות",
      "level_min": "university",
      "body_en_md": "$$SS_{Total}=SS_B+SS_W$$\n\n$$SS_B=\\sum n_i(\\bar x_i-\\bar x)^2,\\quad SS_W=\\sum\\sum(x_{ij}-\\bar x_i)^2$$",
      "body_he_md": "$$SS_{Total}=SS_B+SS_W$$"
    },
    {
      "id": "f_statistic_table",
      "title_en": "F-Statistic and ANOVA Table",
      "title_he": "F וטבלת ANOVA",
      "level_min": "university",
      "body_en_md": "$$MS_B=SS_B/(k-1),\\ MS_W=SS_W/(N-k),\\ F=MS_B/MS_W$$\n\nUnder $H_0$, $F\\sim F(k-1,N-k)$.\n\n| Source | SS | df | MS | F |",
      "body_he_md": "$$F=MS_B/MS_W$$"
    },
    {
      "id": "worked_example",
      "title_en": "Worked Example ? Teaching Methods",
      "title_he": "דוגמה פתורה",
      "level_min": "university",
      "body_en_md": "A,B,C with n=5: means 72,80,90; variances 8. $\\bar x=80$, $SS_B=820$, $SS_W=96$, $F=51.25>3.89$ ? reject $H_0$.",
      "body_he_md": "$F=51.25$ ? דוחים $H_0$"
    },
    {
      "id": "assumptions_posthoc",
      "title_en": "Assumptions and Post-Hoc",
      "title_he": "הנחות ו-Post-Hoc",
      "level_min": "university",
      "body_en_md": "Independence, normality, homoscedasticity (Levene). Post-hoc: Tukey HSD, Bonferroni when $H_0$ rejected.",
      "body_he_md": "Tukey, Bonferroni לזוגות."
    }
  ],
